Legend: **Y** = show | **тАФ** = hide | **╬г** = summary only

| Panel / Table | Catalog | Schema | Table | View | Column | Dataset | Dashboard | Notebook | ML Model | API Endpoint | Stream | Policy | Business Term | Logical Entity | Logical Attribute | Delivery Channel | System |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Costs** | тАФ | тАФ | - | - | тАФ | - | - | тАФ | - | тАФ | - | тАФ | тАФ | тАФ | тАФ | тАФ | - |
